<ul>
  <li>access and manipulate CSS from the Chrome Developer Tools</li>
  <li>use a <code class="highlighter-rouge">layout.erb</code> file in Sinatra for a common structure</li>
  <li>style and position HTML elements using CSS</li>
</ul>

